>while driving around today, i was pondering...
>what makes the fweem sound?

On a Bug, it's probably the pea shooters.  Enough air goes through a
small enough hole to make the whistle.  However, Beetles fweem, Buses
fwoom, per http://www.type2.com/archive/type2/073192.html .

<bentley>This sound occurs when all parts of the engine have been adjusted
to the strict specifications laid down by the Volkswagenwerk.  Deviations
from these specifications are <b>not permissible</b>.</bentley>

